msgid "This utility should only be used in live mode!"
msgstr "Seda utiliiti tuleks kasutada ainult reaalajas režiimis!"

msgid ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting correctly there are no "
"problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='12'>Seda tööriista tuleks kasutada reaalajas režiimis ja Manjaro alglaadimise "
"taastamiseks\n"
"installitud HD-le või SSD-le.</span> <span font='12' foreground='red'>Kui installitud süsteem "
"käivitub õigesti, ei ole alglaadimisel probleeme, nii et see on\n"
"parem mitte jätkata selle tööriista kasutamist.</span> <span font='10' "
"foreground='gray'>Tõenäoliselt töötab ka teiste Linuxi distributsioonidega.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Kas soovite jätkata?\n"
"\n"
"\n"

msgid "Restore Boot, Grub, Initrd and others stuff"
msgstr "Restore Boot, Grub, Initrd ja muud asjad"

msgid "Wait..."
msgstr "Oota..."

msgid "I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"
msgstr "Ma ei leidnud sellesse arvutisse installitud Linuxit, tühistasin protsessi."

msgid ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't find any EFI "
"partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Live-režiimis alglaadimine kasutab EFI-režiimi, kuid <span foreground='red'>ma ei leidnud sellest "
"arvutist ühtegi EFI partitsiooni</span> ,\n"
"tõenäoliselt GRUB taastamine ei toimi.\n"
"\n"
"Proovige taaskäivitada ja arvuti kaudu BIOS teha alglaadimine pärand- või BIOS-režiimis.\n"
"\n"
"Kas soovite proovida isegi vähese tõenäosusega töötada?"

msgid ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Live-režiimis käivitamine kasutab pärandrežiimi, mida nimetatakse ka BIOS-iks,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>kuid leidsin sellest arvutist vähemalt ühe EFI partitsiooni</span>,\n"
"tõenäoliselt GRUB taastamine ei toimi.\n"
"\n"
"Proovige taaskäivitada ja arvuti kaudu BIOS teha alglaadimine EFI-režiimis.\n"
"\n"
"Kas soovite proovida isegi vähese tõenäosusega töötada?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Valige suvand:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Leidsin rohkem kui ühe EFI partitsiooni, valige, millist neist peaks kasutama:"

msgid "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."
msgstr "EFI partitsiooni pole valitud, tühistatud protsess."

msgid "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "
msgstr "Taastage alglaadimine, grub ja initrd "

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one should restore the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Valige suvand:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Leidsin sellesse arvutisse installitud rohkem kui ühe Linuxi, valige, milline neist peaks "
"alglaadimise taastama:"

msgid "No selected partition, canceled process."
msgstr "Valitud partitsiooni pole, tühistatud protsess."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"I found more than one storage device, select which one should record the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Valige suvand:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"Leidsin rohkem kui ühe salvestusseadme, valige, milline neist peaks alglaadimise salvestama:"

msgid "Disk"
msgstr "Ketta"

msgid "Size"
msgstr "Suurus"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "Nimi"

msgid "Partition table"
msgstr "Partitsioonitabel"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>    \n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span>  LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected disk:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk partition table:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk Size:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Andmete kinnitamine</span>:<span font='11' "
"foreground='gray'>Alglaadimisrežiim:</span> LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valitud ketas:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Kettasektsioonide tabel:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Ketta suurus:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valitud partitsioon:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valitud süsteem:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Sektsiooni vorming:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partitsiooni UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Kas soovite jätkata?    \n"
"\n"

msgid "Your computer is not connected to the internet, options 2 and 3 need internet to work."
msgstr "Teie arvuti pole Interneti-ühendusega, 2. ja 3. valikus on töötamiseks vaja Internetti."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways (<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or "
"Complete</span>),if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Valige soovitud valik:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restaureerimist saab teha 3 viisil (<span foreground='gray'>lihtne, vahepealne või täielik</span>), "
"kahtluse korral proovige esimest\n"
"valik, taaskäivitage arvuti ja vaadake, kas see on lahendatud.\n"
"\n"
"Kui probleem püsib, proovige teisi võimalusi."

msgid "Option"
msgstr "Võimalus"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Kirjeldus: __________"

msgid "Simple, just record the grub again at the beginning of the disk."
msgstr "Lihtne, lihtsalt salvestage grub uuesti ketta alguses."

msgid ""
"Intermediate, reinstalls the GRUB package in the partition, generates the configuration and updates "
"Initrd."
msgstr ""
"Vahepealne, installib GRUB-paketi partitsiooni uuesti, genereerib konfiguratsiooni ja värskendab "
"Initrd."

msgid ""
"Complete, performs the stages of the intermediate restoration, updates the system and checks if the "
"LTS kernel is installed."
msgstr ""
"Täielik, teostab vahepealse taastamise etapid, värskendab süsteemi ja kontrollib, kas LTS-kernel on "
"installitud."

msgid "Interactive, opens a terminal within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktiivne, avab terminali valitud süsteemis."

msgid "Interactive, opens a TUI control center within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktiivne, avab valitud süsteemis TUI juhtimiskeskuse."

msgid "Collect useful logs from installed system"
msgstr "Koguge kasulikke logisid installitud süsteemist"

msgid "Interactive, opens the package manager within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktiivne, avab paketihalduri valitud süsteemis."

msgid "Done!"
msgstr "Teinud!"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI partition:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Andmete kinnitamine</span>:<span font='11' "
"foreground='gray'>Käivitusrežiim:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI partitsioon:</span> $EFI_PARTITSIOON\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valitud partitsioon:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valitud süsteem:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Sektsiooni vorming:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partitsiooni UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Kas soovite jätkata?\n"
"    \n"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways(<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or Complete</span>), "
"if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Valige soovitud valik:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Taastamist saab teha 3 viisil<span foreground='gray'>(lihtne, vahepealne või täielik</span>), "
"kahtluse korral proovige esimest\n"
"valik, taaskäivitage arvuti ja vaadake, kas see on lahendatud.\n"
"\n"
"Kui probleem püsib, proovige teisi võimalusi."
